## OpenViking

- URL: http://127.0.0.1:1933
- Account: {{OPENVIKING_ACCOUNT}}
- Key: ~/.claude-lab/shared/secrets/openviking.key

## Kanban (vibe-kanban)

- Launch: `npx vibe-kanban` (opens browser UI)
- MCP: configured in settings.json (auto-available to agent)
- Storage: SQLite (local, no cloud)
- Tasks: each task gets its own git worktree + branch
- Statuses: Todo -> InProgress -> InReview -> Done / Cancelled
- Multi-agent: all agents on same board see the same tasks

## GitHub

- Account: {{GITHUB_USERNAME}}
- CLI: `gh` (authorized)
- Workflow: branches + PR, NEVER push to main

## Secrets (paths only, never values)

- `~/.claude-lab/shared/secrets/` -- all secrets here
- Do NOT output, commit, or copy between servers
